00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:00,820
walang asawa,

991
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:02,260
at walang masamang ugali.

992
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:04,140
Ang impresyon na ibinibigay nila

993
00:43:04,570 --> 00:43:06,080
ay na sila ay tapat, simple,

994
00:43:06,170 --> 00:43:07,190
at masipag.

995
00:43:08,220 --> 00:43:09,240
Nakikita ko ang ibig mong sabihin.

996
00:43:09,750 --> 00:43:10,660
Ang drug trafficker na ito

997
00:43:10,660 --> 00:43:13,460
ay napakapili
kapag pumipili ng downline sellers.

998
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:17,100
Dahil ang grupong ito ng mga nagbebenta

999
00:43:17,740 --> 00:43:18,690
ay napakababa ng profile,

1000
00:43:19,380 --> 00:43:20,940
napakahirap para sa amin

1001
00:43:20,940 --> 00:43:21,780
upang matuklasan ito.

1002
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:25,780
Ngunit itong Yu Susu

1003
00:43:25,780 --> 00:43:26,790
ay hindi pareho

1004
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:28,150
bilang mga taong iyon.

1005
00:43:28,290 --> 00:43:29,810
Hindi mo ba ito nakikitang kakaiba?

1006
00:43:34,620 --> 00:43:35,800
(China Welfare Lottery)
Good luck sa iyo.

1007
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:36,820
Salamat, boss.

1008
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:37,740
Dito.

1009
00:43:39,140 --> 00:43:39,980
Iyong pagbabago.

1010
00:43:48,620 --> 00:43:49,500
Ikaw si Cai diba?

1011
00:43:49,500 --> 00:43:50,710
Galing kami sa police station.

1012
00:43:51,300 --> 00:43:53,420
Gusto naming magtanong sa iyo ng ilang katanungan.

1013
00:43:53,700 --> 00:43:54,610
Direktor Chen,

1014
00:43:55,140 --> 00:43:56,260
kinikilala kita.

1015
00:43:56,400 --> 00:43:58,340
Ano ang gusto mong malaman?

1016
00:43:59,270 --> 00:44:00,320
Kilala mo si Yu Susu?

1017
00:44:00,620 --> 00:44:01,460
ginagawa ko.

1018
00:44:01,820 --> 00:44:02,660
Medyo close kayo?

1019
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:04,100
Hindi naman.

1020
00:44:05,040 --> 00:44:06,400
Pareho kaming taga-Yunchuan.

1021
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:08,820
Mahilig siyang maglaro ng Happy Poker.

1022
00:44:08,820 --> 00:44:09,740
Pagdating niya,

1023
00:44:09,740 --> 00:44:11,030
magkwentuhan lang kami saglit.

1024
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:12,210
Ano ang "Happy Poker"?

1025
00:44:12,500 --> 00:44:13,340
Ito na.

1026
00:44:14,010 --> 00:44:15,370
(Happy Poker, Face Value 2 Yuan)
Scratch ito para manalo ng premyo.

1027
00:44:17,190 --> 00:44:18,340
Kailan ang huling pagkakataon

1028
00:44:18,340 --> 00:44:19,220
nakita mo si Yu Susu?

1029
00:44:19,780 --> 00:44:21,150
Sa tingin ko

1030
00:44:21,620 --> 00:44:23,140
ito ay noong nakaraang buwan.

1031
00:44:25,180 --> 00:44:26,290
Nagtataka ako

1032
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:28,240
bakit hindi siya dumaan lately.

1033
00:44:30,430 --> 00:44:31,420
Anong nangyari sa kanya?

1034
00:44:31,430 --> 00:44:33,330
Meron ba si Yu Susu
may iba pang kakilala sa Fengyang?

1035
00:44:33,340 --> 00:44:34,180
Aba,

1036
00:44:34,180 --> 00:44:35,820
hindi ko talaga alam.

1037
00:44:37,980 --> 00:44:40,500
(Fengyang Bus Station)

1038
00:44:48,540 --> 00:44:49,650
11:45 PM.

1039
00:44:50,300 --> 00:44:51,140
Salamat, bro.

1040
00:44:51,380 --> 00:44:52,500
Huwag mong banggitin.

1041
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:00,420
Kunin mo ito.

1042
00:45:00,420 --> 00:45:01,260
Salamat, Dali.

1043
00:45:01,900 --> 00:45:02,740
Dali,

1044
00:45:02,740 --> 00:45:04,640
sa sandaling umalis ka,
hindi ka na talaga babalik?

1045
00:45:05,900 --> 00:45:06,810
Isang tao sa kanyang salita

1046
00:45:06,810 --> 00:45:07,780
hindi na ito babalikan.

1047
00:45:07,780 --> 00:45:09,400
Ayokong ituloy ang tungkol sa kanya.

1048
00:45:09,680 --> 00:45:10,820
Isa kang tunay na lalaki.

1049
00:45:11,380 --> 00:45:12,220
Sige, alis na ako.

1050
00:45:12,580 --> 00:45:13,420
Ligtas na paglalakbay.

1051
00:45:13,420 --> 00:45:14,260
Manatiling nakikipag-ugnayan.

1052
00:45:25,580 --> 00:45:26,420
Hey, mister.

1053
00:45:27,460 --> 00:45:28,530
Gusto mo bang magsaya?

1054
00:45:29,660 --> 00:45:30,500
magkano?

1055
00:45:31,360 --> 00:45:32,200
Para sa buong gabi,

1056
00:45:33,060 --> 00:45:34,080
isang daan at dalawampu.

1057
00:45:36,020 --> 00:45:38,160
Aalis na ang bus ko ng 11:30 PM.

1058
00:45:38,500 --> 00:45:39,340
Gawin itong mas mura.

1059
00:45:39,740 --> 00:45:42,010
Mister, talagang pinagtatawanan natin ito?

1060
00:45:45,620 --> 00:45:46,500
Mabilis ako,

1061
00:45:47,020 --> 00:45:48,020
mabilis talaga.

1062
00:45:48,980 --> 00:45:49,820
Gawin itong mas mura.

1063
00:45:51,540 --> 00:45:52,740
Fine, tatanggapin ko ang pagkatalo.

1064
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:54,780
Bitawan na kita

1065
00:45:55,580 --> 00:45:56,540
sa 11:30 PM.

1066
00:45:57,100 --> 00:45:57,940
Walumpu.

1067
00:45:58,100 --> 00:45:58,940
Deal.

1068
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:01,380
para saan?

1069
00:46:02,380 --> 00:46:03,220
may pwesto ako.

1070
00:46:23,940 --> 00:46:24,780
ginoo,

1071
00:46:25,660 --> 00:46:26,860
huwag kang magmadali.

1072
00:46:27,820 --> 00:46:29,110
Hayaan mo muna akong magpamasahe.

1073
00:46:36,860 --> 00:46:38,540
Mister, huwag kang magmadali.

1074
00:46:38,540 --> 00:46:40,580
Sir, maghilamos ka muna.

1075
00:46:40,580 --> 00:46:42,320
Maghugas ka muna.

1076
00:46:42,580 --> 00:46:44,220
Hugasan ano? Hindi na kailangan iyon.

1077
00:46:45,220 --> 00:46:46,460
Ang lakas ng loob mong matulog sa asawa ko?

1078
00:46:47,300 --> 00:46:48,140
Patayin siya!

1079
00:46:54,940 --> 00:46:55,940
Sampalin siya ng husto!

1080
00:46:55,940 --> 00:46:56,780
Bugbugin siya hanggang mamatay.

1081
00:46:57,100 --> 00:46:57,980
Anong nagtagal sayo?

1082
00:46:58,380 --> 00:47:00,200
natakot ako
hindi mo pa siya nililigawan.

1083
00:47:00,620 --> 00:47:01,820
Kapag nasa kwarto na sila,

1084
00:47:01,820 --> 00:47:03,020
may hindi ko kayang hawakan?

1085
00:47:07,920 --> 00:47:09,730
Ang isang ito ngayon ay isang malaking customer.

1086
00:47:09,730 --> 00:47:11,170
Oo, iyon ay medyo maraming pera.

1087
00:47:12,050 --> 00:47:12,890
Sige.

1088
00:47:13,080 --> 00:47:13,920
Itigil ang paghampas sa kanya.

1089
00:47:14,220 --> 00:47:15,120
Hayaan mo siyang huminga.

1090
00:47:15,780 --> 00:47:16,700
Tara na.

